05:38.737 --> 05:41.865
<i>Welcome to the world.</i>

05:47.346 --> 05:49.940
Fluctuating
all over the place.

05:50.015 --> 05:54.418
Anywhere we shoot here, it's gonna
be portable gennies and we'll run cable.

06:04.363 --> 06:06.593
- Hello?
- Mike, it's me.

06:06.665 --> 06:09.498
