Breathe deep. Breathe deep.

09:14.685 --> 09:16.482
Slow down, honey. Slow down.

09:16.554 --> 09:19.421
Slow down.

09:19.490 --> 09:22.653
<i>Here we go.</i>
<i>Deep breaths.</i>

09:22.727 --> 09:25.195
