Don't interpret that. Hold it.

14:03.942 --> 14:06.502
Hold it! Hold it!
Slow. Slow.

14:06.578 --> 14:09.240
Sheikh, do you mind?

14:09.314 --> 14:12.078
If you would just turn
your chair a little bit...

14:12.150 --> 14:14.846
to face Mr. Wallace.

14:16.487 --> 14:19.513
- Is that okay?
- Okay.

14:21.159 --> 14:23.855
Are you ready, or do you
wanna keep fucking around...

14:23.928 --> 14:25.862
