Okay, we are rolling.

14:47.151 --> 14:50.314
<i>- Okay, Mike.</i>
- Sheikh Fadlallah.

14:50.388 --> 14:53.448
Thank you so much for seeing us.
Are you a terrorist?

14:54.859 --> 14:58.761
Mr. Wallace, I am
a servant of God.

14:58.830 --> 15:01.924
A servant of God?
Really?

15:02.000 --> 15:05.367
Americans believe that you...
as an Islamic fundamentalist...

15:05.436 --> 15:11.102
