16:54.712 --> 16:57.078
You understand
any of this?

17:00.585 --> 17:02.644
No.

17:03.821 --> 17:06.618
Uh, this looks like
a table of temperatures.

17:06.691 --> 17:10.218
- Who's this from?
- It's anonymous.

17:10.294 --> 17:12.854
References to "P.M."

17:12.930 --> 17:14.954
It's gotta be
Phillip Morris, huh?

17:15.031 --> 17:17.898
Hmm. I have to
take a shower.

17:35.186 --> 17:38.417
Yeah?

17:38.489 --> 17:40.457
Hi. This is
Doug Oliver.

17:40.525 --> 17:42.652
Oh, hi, Doug.
It's Lowell.

17:42.727 --> 17:46.390
I'm doing this story on fire
safety, and people burning up
from falling asleep smoking.

17:46.464 --> 17:50.924
I receive a shitload of scientific
papers from inside Phillip Morris.

17:51.002 --> 17:54.165
Anonymous. You or anybody
in F.D.A. Know someone...

17:54.238 --> 17:56.934
