as a badge of honor you don't
even know what makes water boil.

31:25.780 --> 31:28.271
Well, that's why
we hire scientists.

31:28.349 --> 31:31.648
Okay.

31:31.719 --> 31:34.552
I don't believe that you can
maintain corporate integrity...

31:34.622 --> 31:37.420
without
confidentiality agreements.

31:37.492 --> 31:39.517
I was paid well
for my work,

31:39.594 --> 31:42.620
the health and welfare
benefits are good,

31:42.697 --> 31:45.063
the severance package
is fair.

31:45.133 --> 31:49.092
I have no intention of violating
my confidentiality agreement...

31:49.170 --> 31:52.799
<i>and disclosing that</i>
<i>which I said I wouldn't.</i>

31:54.242 --> 31:56.676
I appreciate
all that, Jeff,

31:56.744 --> 32:02.307
but upon reflection, we've decided
to expand our zone of comfort with you,

32:02.383 --> 32:05.477
so we've drafted a supplement
to your agreement.

32:06.854 --> 32:10.187
<i>It broadly defines and</i>
<i>expands in more detail...</i>

32:10.258 --> 32:12.226
what is confidential.

